{"tid":2290362,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返一套大約20年前上影既電影","createTime":"2020-11-18T03:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T07:24:39.000Z","uid":40300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f57a7d927e4f399a8421ffae911caf14921b0d07","tid":2290362,"uid":40300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"電影係20幾年前上影, 好似係鑽石山廣場睇<br />\n<br />\n亞洲人演 (香港, 日本, 內地唔肯定, 應該係香港)<br />\n對白係廣東話, 係唔係配音唔記得..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事發生現代, 講述一位Man(20尾 至 30歲左右 中等身材) + 一位Boy(幼稚園/小學生) 一齊生活既故事<br />\n<br />\n印象中 Man係因為一啲事接左Boy一齊住, 係唔係父子關係已經唔記得。<br />\n<br />\n過程同結局又唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係有一幕好深刻<br />\n<br />\n夜晚景，<br />\nMan 著白色背心 同Boy 係 天台鐵皮(或 游艇面)　訓係度，面向上；<br />\n<br />\nBoy : 果粒咩星啊?<br />\nMam : 瀨屎星 (定痾屎星, 重知係同屎有關)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇師兄睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cb6a8491257180a753312d4d980b74de1584d4","tid":2290362,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:09:43.000Z","msg":"咁似張國榮套流星語"},{"pid":"1d7bd6719a79b0cf4ce4431687c08d046c5789a2","tid":2290362,"uid":40300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02cb6a8491257180a753312d4d980b74de1584d4","tid":2290362,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:09:43.000Z","msg":"咁似張國榮套流星語"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"好似真係，個feel好似<br />\n<br />\n巴大勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，揾日睇下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"}]}